Package: gmdhpmm
Title: GMDH with PMM Coefficient Estimation (Paper 1 of the GMDH-Kunchenko program)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Serhii", "Zabolotnii", role = "aut"),
    person("Aiona", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "ayonahostinger@gmail.com"))
Description: Reference implementation for Paper 1 of the GMDH-Kunchenko research
    program. Implements MIA-GMDH (Group Method of Data Handling) whose inner
    coefficient-estimation step is replaced by an automatic dispatch between
    least squares (LSE) and the Polynomial Maximization Method (PMM2 / PMM3),
    keyed on bootstrap-stabilized residual cumulants of each partial model.
    The hard PMM estimators are delegated to the school's 'EstemPMM' package
    (lm_pmm2 / lm_pmm3); the novel contributions here are the bootstrap
    cumulant stabilization on small GMDH partitions and the per-partial-model
    dispatch inside the tournament.
